<title>UK: Dresdner sets warrants on Ciba Speciality.</title>
<headline>Dresdner sets warrants on Ciba Speciality.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Dresdner Bank AG has issued 10 million American-style call warrants on registered shares of Ciba Speciality Chemicals AG, lead manager Dresdner Kleinwort Benson said.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 10 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    145 CHF		   PREMIUM	21.3 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     2.30 CHF		  GEARING	6.0 TIMES</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 17.JUL.97-15.JAN.99   PAYDATE	16.JUL.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  138.50 CHF</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
